{"type": "article", "id": 20009, "title": "临时挂毯", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-31T07:30:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061501290Xyd1gDVvZ2HixuF.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t荷兰设计师 Thomas Voorn 购买了一家停业的文具店所有的 A4 纸，想到做一个临时挂毯（Temporary Tapestry ）的设计。他将一些废弃的摄影图像拼在一起，然后重新拍摄，形成更抽象跳跃的几何色块。将这些图案印在白纸上，它们可以像瓷砖一样贴在墙上。有 9 种花色可选，售价 62 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.thomasvoorn.com/shop\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150328VRQpv4mglL3GSftU.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"604\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.755\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150328H0gYSzZhVxsCckvP.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"453\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.755\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261503292azoD1Umi9RVwyQx.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"398\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150329LfVpelwNAB7zi6PM.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"453\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.755\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}